{
  "epId": 3451,
  "name": "羽生田千鹤",
  "desc": "<p>依物品而诞生的妖怪，在本体之外幻化出人类的外形，是一位「付丧神」。</p>",
  "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/09/142453215/8c5b3611d8309efd5945e2cf8e327acc_2811811937742924851.png",
